<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw, tu'n ka mui thienna lui chuh!
 Luikhuk thuk leh lien chuh;
 Ka Lal Isu'n A hukdam thei,
 A nak liemna apat.

[V2]
 Thienna lui chuh ka mui, ka mui!
 Ka kidieh, aw ei silthieng tai;
 Lalpa pak un, ei silthieng tai,
 Ei silthieng tai, ei silthieng tai.

[V3]
 2. Thilsiem thak a hungum ka mu'i,
 Thisan thugen ka za'i;
 Thu a gen hindan lui a thii,
 Thisan luiah tummang.

[V4]
 3. Van vaka leng dingin ka tho,
 Gitloh, khawvel chungah;
 Lunggil thieng puon, puonvam silh in,
 Ziechun Kristan vaihawm.

[V5]
 4. Lungsietna mak vana kipan,
 A thisan lun pie di'n;
 Isu, Amah maiin a hei,
 Khetdena um Isu.</lyrics>
<title>THE CLEANSING WAVE</title>
</song>